➜重阳情深，好诗共品（斌心学校）
http://www.sohu.com/a/428037015_458565	3714
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201029/f998463e3454460585c5eaf0bb3b2b77.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>诉衷情</strong></p>
<p><strong>·芙蓉金菊斗馨香</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宋代 晏殊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">芙蓉金菊斗馨香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天气欲重阳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远村秋色如画，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红树间疏黄。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流水淡，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">碧天长。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">路茫茫。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凭高目断。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸿雁来时，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无限思量。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201029/95619794d14c41098934d32f9b7af5cf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
